Save entertainment_center.py, fresh_tomatoes.py and media.py in the same folder - example movies.
Open entertainment_center.py with python by launching idle.
Select Run
entertainment_center.py creates and automatically launches an HTML file called fresh_tomatoes.html.
This HTML file is stored and can be opened from the movies folder you created

Any changes to the Movie Library should be done on the entertainment_center.py file.
Any changes to the HTML should be done on the fresh_tomatoes.py file
